            class="animated text-2xl md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold capitalize text-black dark:text-white text-center"
          >
            Design partners <br/> for next-gen tech
          </p>
          <p class="animated text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg opacity-75">
            From Prototype to Launchpad, Design Solutions to Fuel for Your Tech
            Product
          </p>
          <div
            id="ctaButtons"
            class="animated flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center pt-5"
          >
            <a
              href="https://topmate.io/madhuri_basant/852589"
              target="_blank"
