          <p class="text-sm text-center">
            We are experienced in handling high-pressure situations and ensure
            we can maintain focus and deliver quality work under tight
            deadlines.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="" class="h-[200vh] md:h-[150vh] bg-black">
